'''NovaNetwork''', also known as '''Nova Network''', was a news agency during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Civil War]]. It was the arch-rival of [[TriNebulon News/Legends|TriNebulon News]]. NovaNetwork managed to be pro-Imperial and still have sympathy towards individual rights, though many considered them to be "bottom-feeders". They were on the list of legitimate targets for [[Rebel privateer]]s. The Nova Network's headquarters was in the [[Column Commons]] District of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].

